text: Jamilya () is a 1968 Soviet drama movie directed by Irina Poplavskaya.Московский кинотеатр "Иллюзион" покажет 17-26 августа ретроспективу экранизаций АйтматоваДЖАМИЛЯ (1968) It stars Natalya Arinbasarova, Suymenkul Chokmorov, and Nasreddin Dubashev. == Actors == * Natalya Arinbasarova as Jaamilya * Suymenkul Chokmorov as Daniyar * Nasreddin Dubashev * Aliman Zhankorozova as Dzhanyl * Altynbek Kenzhekov as Sadyk * Mukhtar Bakhtygereyev as Osmon * Bolot Beyshenaliev as Khudozhnik == References == ==Other websites== * Category:1968 drama movies Category:Soviet drama movies
title: Jamilya (1968 movie)
